{
  "text": "To obtain further insights into PCPE-1 in vivo roles, we have begun examining the characteristics of Pcolce \u2212/\u2212 soft tissues. Evidence of PCPE-1 corneal expression [CITATION_1] ), the facility for observation and experimental manipulation of this tissue and the profound effects that corneal scarring associated with abnormal collagen deposition, has led to the current study on effects of PCPE-1 ablation on responses to corneal injury.",
